This paper is about image captioning, which is a task in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper introduces a novel technique for caption generation using neural-symbolic encoding, which involves the use of natural language processing techniques (cs.CL) and machine learning algorithms (cs.AI, cs.LG). The paper also discusses attention mechanisms, which are commonly used in information retrieval (cs.IR).
